  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Deaf Children learn to read and write</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DID YOU KNOW that deaf children make up an illiterate and excluded population? In Argentina, Spanish is their second language, but there are no materials for them to learn how to to read and write. To prevent school desertion and to match their opportunities to access culture, we will elaborate a textbook for deaf children to become literate. Literacy is a gateway to the world.</narrative>
  </description>
